  "content": "<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>16. Who had access to those accounts before or after death?</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>17. Any recent withdrawals, closures, or suspicious transfers?</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>18. Any signs of forgery, digital access, or impersonation?</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>19. Were any new beneficiaries added to accounts pre-death?</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>19b. Any life insurance or retirement accounts?</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>19c. Who are the listed beneficiaries, and were they changed recently?</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>",
